        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Contains pamphlets, writings and reports pertaining to the research interests of Charles Davis. Included are a number of United States Agriculture Department reports, pamphlets and other materials on Pittsburgh's urban planning, and research project material on women workers in Brazil. The materials span from the 1920s to the 1940s. PLEASE DIRECT FURTHER INQUIRIES TO: peter.filardo@nyu.edu</p>
        </scopecontent>
